    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver 414 hp with a redline of 8,400 RPM. The 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a functional M-variable differential for optimal power delivery. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including the replacement of rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014essential for long-term S65 reliability. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), maintaining excellent damping characteristics across all modes. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with enthusiast use, the powertrain and subframe remain robust, offering a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
